flowRoot.flowPara: Google Summer of Code is a global program that offers student developers stipends to write FOSS code. The goal is to inspire young developers to begin participating in open source development and to help open source projects bring in new developers. It provides students the opportunity to do work related to their academic pursuits during the summer.
